Package: mygestures
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Modern mouse gestures utility for Wayland and Evdev
 MyGestures is a tool that allows you to perform actions by drawing
 gestures with your mouse, touchpad, or touchscreen. It works directly
 with evdev and uinput, making it compatible with Wayland compositors
 like Sway, Hyprland, and GNOME/KDE.
